a1 6
# OpenBSD makefile for:	xminehunter
# Version required:	0.4
# Date created:		May 19 1998
# Whom:			Angelos D. Keromytis
#
# $OpenBSD: Makefile,v 1.1.1.1 1998/05/20 01:58:18 angelos Exp $
